               <p>RICHARD BOWDEN. I am a <rs id="t18280410-238-viclabel1272" type="occupation">hatter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-238-victim1328 t18280410-238-viclabel1272"></join>. On the 22d of February the prisoner was brought into my shop with this hat, which he had taken from my door - he said he was in distress, and did not care what became of him; I gave him a shilling and let him go; he was afterwards taken by the street-keeper.</p>
               <p>
            
